RACS (Remote Agent Context Store) is a universal, zero-runtime-dependency
library and CLI for provider-faithful prefix-cache management: stability
linting, multi-provider directive planning, deterministic prefix keys,
TTL keep-warm scheduling, drift detection, persistence, and hit-ratio and
savings analytics. It never calls a provider API.

